			<div class="comment-body"><p>I just made this marshmallow recipe and found that if you beat 2 egg whites  till they reach stiff peaks and then add that when you mix in your vanilla extract that it makes these even more fluffy and delicious! Also, I used 1 scraped vanilla bean along with the vanilla extract to make these vanilla bean marshmallows&#8230;. delicious!</p>
